<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="109v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l11">Frawn Elıſabethen von Cleue vnd von der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l12">Marıch . <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒogin</expan> in Payern wıtıben </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l13">Gnedıge fraw als vns eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der kleynet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l14"> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe <expan>etlıch<ex>en</ex></expan> Juden bey vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_219_line_1576673621531_10543">
<del rend="strikethrough">vo </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſteen </del> von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ſteen VVıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l17">dıe frıſt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_219_line_1576673677060_10596">dıe wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_219_line_1576673680445_10601"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> <expan>ludweıg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_219_line_1576673683127_10606"> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> ſune </ab></add> auf ſand Mıchelſtag nehſt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_219_r1l15"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>angeſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> ʒu kurcʒ ſey . vnd eınr <expan>leng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l19">frıſt <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> auf ſand Merteıns tag etc / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l21">Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Juden für vns beſant . vnd <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu eren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l22">ſo <expan>u<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mıt Jn gerett / daʒ ſıe dıe <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> kleynet . bıs auf ſand / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l25">merteins tag ſchıerıſt <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>kawft</expan> halten 
<add><ab facs="#facs_219_line_1576673645118_10566"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> / Alſo daʒ ſıe hinfür </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l26">von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden noch von <expan>nıema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> von <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vmb keın </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l27"><expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> frıſt mer <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . als auch vns das eẅr gnade <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l28">nemlıch <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_219_r1l29"><expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_219" id="109v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Elisabethen von Cleve und von der Marich,
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czogin</expan> in Payern, witiben </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns ewr
                                                  <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der
                                                kleynet <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> die
                                                  <expan>etlich<ex>en</ex></expan> juden bey uns von
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> steen, wie die frist,
                                                  <add>die wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Ludweig<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> sune,</add> auf <app><note><q type="date">sand
                                                      Michelstag nehst</q>29.09.1415</note></app> <add><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>angeschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan></add> zu kurcz sey,
                                                und einr <expan>leng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> frist
  <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> auf <app><note><q type="date">sand Merteins
  tag</q>11.11.1415</note></app> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> juden für uns
                                                besant und <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu eren so
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit in gerett, daz
                                                sie die <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> kleynet
                                          bis auf sand Merteins tag schierist
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>kawft</expan> halten
                                                  <add><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n,</expan></add> also
                                                daz sie hinfür von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                                                gnaden noch von <expan>niema<ex>n</ex>ts</expan> von
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> umb kein
                                                  <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> frist mer
                                                  <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, als auch uns das ewr
                                                gnade <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> nemlich
                                                  <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat; denn wo
                                                wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                                                  <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
